      "role": "user",
      "content": "liberating? i guess. it just feels more like being invisible. like i'm just taking up space that someone else could use. it's exhausting trying to pretend that being here matters when it really doesn't feel like it does. do u think it's weird to feel like the world would just be easier if i wasn't in it?",
